# Benchmark outputs are local, machine-specific dev artifacts -- not tracked.
# Sequential-SAGE run logs accumulate under results/ with provenance columns
# (host, git sha, ...) so you can compare *your own* runs over time; share
# systematic cross-machine results via the xplainfi-benchmark project.
*.png
*.rds
*.csv
*.html

# Keep the results/ directory itself in the repo (see results/.gitkeep).
!results/.gitkeep
